snippet.title: CANDY CHICKEN | Chicken Popsicle | Crispy Chicken Snack Recipe Cooking in Village | Bread Recipe
snippet.description: Watch how we make CANDY CHICKEN ‚Äì a fun and crispy chicken popsicle snack cooked in traditional village style! Juicy chicken is marinated with village spices, wrapped like a lollipop, coated with a crispy bread layer, and deep-fried to golden perfection. This is a must-try recipe for chicken lovers and a perfect evening snack for kids and adults alike. Don‚Äôt miss the unique cooking method and mouth-watering village flavors in every bite!

snippet.title: ‡ÆÆ‡Øä‡Æ±‡ØÅ ‡ÆÆ‡Øä‡Æ±‡ØÅ ‡Æâ‡Æ≥‡ØÅ‡Æ®‡Øç‡Æ§‡ØÅ ‡Æµ‡Æü‡Øà & ‡Æµ‡Øá‡Æ∞‡Øç‡Æï‡Æü‡Æ≤‡Øà ‡Æö‡Æü‡Øç‡Æ©‡Æø | Medu Vada & Peanut Chutney | Chef Deena's Kitchen
snippet.description:
Urad dal Vadai  
Kumbakonam's culinary gold! Imagine the aroma of freshly fried vadais and the vibrant flavors of homemade chutney. Chef Deena takes us on a culinary journey to Kumbakonam, where he meets Mr. Sakthi Krishnan of Shree Vinayaga Catering Services, a master of traditional South Indian cooking. Prepare to be inspired as they share the secrets behind their irresistible Medhu Vadai and Peanut Chutney.  The intricate techniques and regional nuances that make these dishes truly exceptional are elaborated in this video

Recipe by Mr. Sakthi Krishnan - 94431 61929
Sri Vinayaka Catering Service.
No 67, Bakthapuri Street, Kumbakonam.
Landmark : Near by Court Rounding, Next to V.K Thirumana mandapam .

Medhuvada
Urad Dal - 1/4 Kg
Green Chilli - 2 Nos.
Chopped Ginger - 2 Tbsp 
Chopped Carrot - 2 Tbsp
Rice Flour - As Required 
Coriander Leaves - Few Springs 
Curry Leaves - Few Strings 
Pepper - 1 Tsp
Asafoetida - 1 Tsp
Salt - To Taste
Oil - For Fry

Peanut Chutney

Peanuts - 100g
Ginger - As Required 
Garlic - 2 Cloves
Dry Red Chilli - 3 Nos. 
Grated Coconut - 50g 
Tamarind - A Small 
Piece Salt - To Taste
Shallots - For Tempering 
Mustard - 1 Tsp
Curry Leaves - For Tempering 
Oil - For Tempering


My Amazon Store { My Picks and Recommended Product }
https://www.amazon.in/shop/chefdeenaskitchen

_______________
Hello!!  My Name is chef Deena from the popular Adupangarai show in Jaya TV Viewers must have seen me in Zee Tamil shows as well.  My Culinary journey as a trainee to become an Executive Chef is incredible. My experience in the culinary field is for more than fifteen years and my USP is Indian cooking !! Apart from being a TV cookery host, my experience lies mainly with being employed in some of the major star hotels across the country especially the Marriott group.

     Chef Deena Cooks is my English Youtube Channel! Practical, simple recipes are my forte and using minimal easily available ingredients is my hallmark. Rudiments of cooking and baking are taught from scratch and any amateur cook can learn to make exciting dishes by watching my channel!  Also, Cooking traditional foods, Easy cooking Recipes, Healthy Snacks, Indian curries, gravies, Baking and Millions of other homemade treats. 

Subscribe to Chef Deena Cooks (CDK) for more cooking videos.

snippet.description:
Gokuldham Society | Gada Electronics | Bonus | Financial Year

Step into Jethalal‚Äôs world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun. Are you ready for the challenge? 

 Play now: https://gadaelectronics.page.link/dhgB  #GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada

snippet.title: Ek Date Aisi Bhi | Take A Break
snippet.description:
In Ek Date Aisi Bhi, join three friends as they set out on what they think will be the perfect romantic dates‚Ä¶ only for everything to go hilariously wrong! üò¨üíî
From awkward silences and weird restaurant choices to unexpected ex-encounters and disastrous conversations, each date turns into a comedy of errors. But just when all hope seems lost, a surprising twist brings unexpected connections and a dash of real love into the mix.
Full of laughs, relatable moments, and a sweet message, this sketch proves that sometimes, even the worst dates can lead to the best stories.‚ù§Ô∏è

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

#GhumHaiKisikeyPyaarMein #GHKKPM #SaasBahuAurSaazish #SBS #aditiarorasawant 

In Ghum Hai Kisikey Pyaar Meiin, the character Savi is introduced as Sai and Virat‚Äôs daughter. Savi brings a new dimension to the story as she becomes a bridge and a source of emotional complexity between her estranged parents, Sai and Virat. Her presence challenges Virat's loyalty to his family and reignites unresolved feelings between him and Sai. Rajat is another recent character who brings twists to the plot, affecting the dynamics between the main characters and creating new conflicts. Both Savi and Rajat play pivotal roles in evolving the storyline, deepening the emotional layers of the show, and introducing new conflicts that keep the characters‚Äîand viewers‚Äîon their toes.

Watch Saas Bahu aur Saazish (SBS) on ABP News daily at 2:30 PM to know what's happening in Indian television and bollywood industry with Aditi Arora Sawant. snippet.description:
Dhyan Sreenivasan Crashes Annie‚Äôs Kitchen! üòÇüçç Vishu Special with a Sweet Twist!

This Vishu, Annie's Kitchen is filled with laughter, surprises, and sweet moments as the charming Dhyan Sreenivasan joins Annie for a festive feast! üéâ

Annie starts off the celebration by preparing a special Vishu Pradhaman, a rich and delicious payasam that sets the mood just right. But the real surprise? Dhyan walks in as a guest and stuns Annie with his unexpected visit! üò≤üíõ

As Annie plans to treat Dhyan with a grand Vishu Sadya, she suddenly realizes she forgot to make kichadi ‚Äì specifically the pineapple version she had in mind. That‚Äôs when Dhyan steps in with full spirit, offering to help her in the kitchen! üççüë®‚Äçüç≥

Get ready for a cooking session packed with witty puns, playful banter, and heartwarming conversations as Annie and Dhyan team up to whip up the perfect Pineapple Kichadi. Along the way, Dhyan opens up about his latest projects, personal updates, and of course, adds his signature humor to every moment.

Don‚Äôt miss this fun-filled, flavor-packed Vishu Special Episode of Annie‚Äôs Kitchen! üåº‚ú®

"Annie's Kitchen" is a unique and exciting cookery-cum-chat show, airing every Friday at 8 PM on Amrita TV. In its second season, this delightful program is hosted by the multi-talented and charming Annie Shaji Kailas, a well-known actress in the Indian film industry. Join Annie as she whips up delicious and mouth-watering dishes in the kitchen, showcasing her culinary skills while inviting celebrity guests from the world of entertainment to join her.

                The show is divided into two engaging segments. In the first segment, watch as Annie demonstrates how to prepare a special dish, adding her personal touch and sharing handy cooking tips that will leave you craving more. In the second segment, the real fun begins! Annie sits down for a lively and entertaining chat with her celebrity guests, asking them humorous, intriguing  questions that reveal fascinating stories from their lives and careers.

                                         Annie, who is married to renowned filmmaker Shaji Kailas, brings a perfect blend of warmth and wit to every episode. Together, they have become a beloved couple in the industry, and Annie‚Äôs playful charm and insightful interviews make "Annie's Kitchen" a must-watch for viewers of all ages.

Annies Kitchen Let's Cook with Love | Friday @ 8 pm  |Amrita TV
